675
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,530
I just doodled.

676
00:36:03,050 --> 00:36:04,530
If the Prefect can't understand it,

677
00:36:04,690 --> 00:36:06,420
I can explain it.

678
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:07,780
No need.

679
00:36:08,570 --> 00:36:09,420
I believe

680
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:11,420
you are indeed the chief's disciple.

681
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:14,250
My Lord, you can't trust him.

682
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:15,280
