703
00:37:14,780 --> 00:37:16,610
who framed Master Jingming.

704
00:37:21,860 --> 00:37:23,250
- This...
- Father.

705
00:37:23,250 --> 00:37:25,170
Shen Jiangli must've tampered with it.

706
00:37:25,420 --> 00:37:27,020
How could I possibly frame Jingming?

707
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:28,340
Master Jingxiu,

708
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:31,250
